em_assets/steam/apps/1752250/extras/0923d474b21abfb9820ffdf8f0836076.mp4?t=1679690596\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Bathe the cat using your logical thinking and physic intuition.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Create and destroy dams to channel a fluid so that it reaches the cat.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Experience several kind of fluids with different mechanics (Water, Lava, Gas).</strong><br></li><li> <strong>Use bombs to make a fluid reach difficult places.</strong><br></li><li> <strong>40 unique handmade levels.</strong></li></ul>",
